title: Babuschken - Babuschken
description:
The AWESOME band Babuschken's first (and probably last) single.

Babuschken is originally a bush from the campsite of Hultsfredsfestivalen who was used for peeing purposes the summer of 2k4, and this song is a kind of sheer for the bush.

There is another song from the band, it's called "Jeppe freebasar sitt ollon" and if we find the time to hook up this old ass computer we will share it with you guys.
